727842ee35117d804f72ed9be380babed26701b6fdac4dab0a679e388982fb35  result/rootfs.tar.gz
# Rebaselined 2026-07-15 after making the FULL build (base + os-image)
# reproducible end-to-end.
#
# Deterministic repack: build/rootfs/apply-stages.nix and build/rootfs/tarball.nix
# tar with --sort=name --mtime=@1700000000 (SOURCE_DATE_EPOCH) and pigz/gzip -n,
# so entry order, timestamps and the gzip header no longer vary across rebuilds.
# --numeric-owner is kept and --owner/--group are intentionally NOT forced to 0
# (the rootfs legitimately contains non-root files, e.g. /home/vcap = 1000/1000).
#
# Base ephemeral scrub (build/rootfs/tarball.nix postInstall): the base image
# shipped install-time ephemeral files whose CONTENT is random per build and
# survived into the os-image. They are now removed/emptied before tarring and
# regenerated at runtime:
#   - /etc/ssh/ssh_host_{rsa,ecdsa,ed25519}_key(.pub)  (firstboot: ssh-keygen -A)
#   - /etc/machine-id                                   (emptied; systemd/misc-os)
#   - /etc/nvme/hostid, /etc/nvme/hostnqn               (regenerated by OS)
#   - /var/cache/ldconfig/aux-cache                     (regenerated by ldconfig)
#   - /var/lib/dbus/machine-id                          (regenerated on boot)
#   - /var/log/{dpkg,alternatives}.log                  (runtime logs, truncated)
#
# Base qcow2 dropped (build/rootfs/tarball.nix postVM): the underlying
# fillDiskWithDebs VM emitted an unused $out/disk-image.qcow2 (ext4 working disk)
# whose UUID/block layout/unscrubbed state varied every build. Only rootfs.tar.gz
# is consumed downstream (apply-stages.nix), so postVM removes the qcow2 after the
# VM exits.
#
# Verified reproducible:
#   nix build .#noble-rootfs --rebuild  -> exit 0 (base)
#   nix build .#os-image      --rebuild -> exit 0 (folded stemcell rootfs)
#
# Tree vs pre-scrub golden (f8px5nwjka92...-os-image): the ONLY differences are
# the intended scrubs above (removed regenerable files + two emptied logs); all
# other paths match by content/mode/owner.
#
# Prior hashes: a0209c8b... (pre base-scrub, base still cached), 4eee73a9...
# (stale after the co-location refactor).
